Package ru.tinkoff.qa.neptune.core.api.steps

Annotation Type SequentialGetStepSupplier.DefaultParameterNames

  • @Retention(RUNTIME)
@Target(TYPE)
public static @interface SequentialGetStepSupplier.DefaultParameterNames
    This annotation is designed to mark subclasses of SequentialGetStepSupplier. It is used for the reading of timeouts, polling intervals, from-values, criteria and for the forming of parameters of a resulted step-function.
    See Also:
    SequentialGetStepSupplier.timeOut(Duration), SequentialGetStepSupplier.pollingInterval(Duration), SequentialGetStepSupplier.criteria(Criteria), SequentialGetStepSupplier.criteria(String, Predicate), SequentialGetStepSupplier.from(Object), SequentialGetStepSupplier.from(SequentialGetStepSupplier), SequentialGetStepSupplier.from(Function)
